step.1-->The first step is it is important to install necessary packages

       npm install ngx-toastr --save
       npm install @angular/animations --save

Note:After installing the above two packages we need follow the following steps 
**we can add toaster service in 2 methods.here I will explain the method1**

Step.2 -->> In angular project --> In the "style.css" file  add the below one at the top (that means at 1st line)

       @import 'ngx-toastr/toastr';

step.3-->>In "app.module.ts" file import theses two  1.BrowserAnimationsModule  and 2.ToastrModule like below 

       import { BrowserAnimationsModule } from '@angular/platform-browser/animations';
       import { ToastrModule } from 'ngx-toastr';

       and also in @NgModule imports like below 

       @NgModule({
         imports: [ 
            BrowserAnimationsModule, -->> like this 
            ToastrModule.forRoot(),  -->>
            ],
step.4-->After above 3 steps you have to import the toasteservice in which component you want to use the toaster service 
         in your angular application
         ** like below we need to do for working of a toaster

         import { ToastrService } from 'ngx-toastr';      *** like this need to import ***
         @Component({...})
         export class YourComponent {
         constructor(private toastr: ToastrService) {}    *** important to define it is in the constractor to use ***

         showSuccess() {
          this.toastr.success('Hello world!', 'Toastr fun!');   *** like this we use the toaster service to display the messages***
         }
         }

NOTE: After following the above steps the toaster will work. but may get problem like not able display the message in the center of the 
      Screen. to resolve it follow the below steps.

Step.1-->> In "app.module.ts" we need to right like below. the toaster service has lot of properties like we can define time to display 
            the message (how much time it should display)

          ToastrModule.forRoot({
           preventDuplicates: true,   *** it prevents to display the message multiple time ***
           positionClass:'toast-top-center' *** by using this we set the position to display the message ***
         })
NOTE: generally by using the above one it will display the message our desired position. if it is not working for the to display it on the 
      top-center.then follow the bellow one.

step1.1 In the "style.css"  file add this code  this will work .it display the message top to the center of the screen 

                             .toast-top-center {
                              top: 12px;
                              right: 0;
                              bottom: auto;
                              left: 50%;
                              transform: translateX(-50%);
                              -webkit-transform: translateX(-50%);
                              -moz-transform: translateX(-50%);
                              -ms-transform: translateX(-50%);
                              -o-transform: translateX(-50%);
                              }


******* below one is the reference link how to use the toaster service in angular In which they provided step bystep process to use 
               toaster service ********

        Link: https://www.npmjs.com/package/ngx-toastr
       

